  "title": "Key Account Manager - SS10",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Account Manager (Solar Energy)</strong></p><ul><li>Working Location: Nearest MRT: Mattar</li><li>Working Days: Monday - Friday</li><li>Working Hours: 9am - 6pm</li><li>Salary Range:  $3200 - $4000</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>• Manage the structuring and negotiation of solar leasing and turnkey agreements</p><p>• Prepare financial model to assess the returns of the project</p><p>• Prepare, submit proposal/tender bids, follow-up and carry out tender presentations</p><p>• Achieve the required sales targets of solar PV project</p><p>• Work closely with Solar Project Management & O&M team and EPC contractors on project management and to follow through the development and implementation of solar PV projects</p><p>• Develop strong relationship with C&I customers, SP Services, regulatory and government bodies, and key stakeholders</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>• Minimum a Bachelor’s Degree in Engineering, Finance or relevant field</p><p>• Preferably with minimum two (2) years of relevant work experience in energy industry or renewable products</p><p>• Experience and knowledge of reviewing Financial Modelling<br /></p><p>Samuel Siaw</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd</p><p>EA No: 14C7279</p><p>Reg No: R2412474</p>",
